name: URANUS
description: The project is a meme coin around the idea of Elon Musk talking about eventually reaching Uranus after he reaches Mars. As Elon discussed his eventual goal of reaching Uranus, this project was launched and quickly abandoned by the dev. It was taken over by the community and is now ran entirely by them. There is no utility, only the simple idea of bringing people together in a strong community over the idea of human beings becoming an interplanetary species.
